<li>Best Sound (<a href="/w/index.php?title=Mark_Berger_(sound_designer)&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Mark Berger (sound designer) (page does not exist)">Mark Berger</a>, <a href="/w/index.php?title=Thomas_Scott_(sound_designer)&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Thomas Scott (sound designer) (page does not exist)">Thomas Scott</a>, <a href="/w/index.php?title=Todd_Boekelheide&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Todd Boekelheide (page does not exist)">Todd Boekelheide</a> and <a href="/wiki/Chris_Newman_(sound_engineer)" title="Chris Newman (sound engineer)">Christopher Newman</a>)</li>
