<p><a name="BAFTA" id="BAFTA"></a></p>
<h4><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Amadeus_(film)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=16" title="Edit section: BAFTA">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline"><a href="/wiki/British_Academy_of_Film_and_Television_Arts" title="British Academy of Film and Television Arts">BAFTA</a></span></h4>
