</ul>
<dl>
<dd>
<ul>
<li>Best Cinematography (Miroslav Ondříček)</li>
<li>Best Editing (Nena Danevic and Michael Chandler)</li>
<li>Best Make Up Artist (Dick Smith and Paul LeBlanc)</li>
<li>Best Sound (<a href="/wiki/Mark_Berger" title="Mark Berger">Mark Berger</a>, <a href="/wiki/Thomas_Scott" title="Thomas Scott">Thomas Scott</a> and <a href="/wiki/Chris_Newman_(sound_engineer)" title="Chris Newman (sound engineer)">Christopher Newman</a>)</li>
</ul>
</dd>
</dl>
<ul>
<li>Nominated</li>
</ul>
<dl>
<dd>
<ul>
<li>Best Actor (F. Murray Abraham)</li>
<li>Best Costume Design (Theodor Pištěk)</li>
<li>Best Film (Miloš Forman and <a href="/wiki/Saul_Zaentz" title="Saul Zaentz">Saul Zaentz</a>)</li>
<li>Best Production Design (Patrizia von Brandstein)</li>
<li>Best Screenplay - Adapted (Peter Shaffer)</li>
</ul>
</dd>
</dl>
